growthexperiments-newcomertasks-config-m:
Error message when the on-wiki task configuration page has a missing field. Parameters:
* $1 - Name of missing field
* $2 - Task type which has the error.
growthexperiments-newcomertasks-config-i:
Error message when the on-wiki task configuration page has an invalid group (difficulty) specification. Parameters:
* $1 - Name of missing field
* $2 - Task type which has the error.
growthexperiments-newcomertasks-config-m:
Error message when the required system messages do not exist for one of the configured task types. Parameters:
* $1 - Name of missing field
* $2 - Task type which has the error.
